        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">I use root-dot to begin with to get mobs down to under half health.  Then once root drops I fear them and stick pet to finish them off, thereby ensuring I get full exp.  Pet is also handy for those adds, 49 pet can tank them for a short while to give you a chance to get fear and darkness on it whilst you leave the original mob rooted and loaded with DoTs.</P><P>Using this technique I have managed to take down 3 mobs simultaneously when I got jumped once.  Just keep that lich running all the time....</P><P><BR>Draknn Fels, Level 53 Erudite Necromancer<BR>Divide et Impera, Bristlebane<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
